From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.

Rachel Sarah Bilson (born August 25, 1981 height 5' 2" (1,57 m)) is an American actress. Bilson grew up in a California show business family, and made her television debut in 2003, subsequently becoming well-known for playing Summer Roberts on the prime time drama series The O.C. Bilson made her film debut in the 2006 film The Last Kiss and starred in the 2008 action/science fiction film Jumper.
